parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience sudden shutdowns, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
the battery warning light illuminates
the service charging system warning light appears
the vehicle loses power
and the engine control module fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the charging system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience sudden shutdowns, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery warning light illuminates
the service charging system warning light appears
the vehicle loses power
and the battery needs to be replaced frequently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the StabilTrak system can cause the vehicle to lose traction, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The StabilTrak warning light illuminates
the vehicle loses power steering
and the vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience sudden shutdowns, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
the engine control module fails
and the vehicle has difficulty starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the trunk can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to accidents if the trunk opens while driving.
symptoms: The trunk pops open while driving or parked intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear toe link suspension can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle drifts or zigzags while driving
the vehicle decelerates inadvertently
the check engine warning light is illuminated
the vehicle shakes or is hard to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic stability control system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The stability tracking light comes on randomly
the transmission kicks and jerks
the electronic brake light comes on
the vehicle comes to a stop in traffic.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front sway bar can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The front sway bar fractures
the vehicle is difficult to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates on its own
the vehicle passes through a parking lot lane
over two curbs
and scrapes a small post in the parking lot.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the StabilTrak system can cause the vehicle to lose power, resulting in sudden changes in vehicle handling and deceleration, particularly at higher speeds, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The StabilTrak warning light illuminates
the vehicle loses power
the steering wheel becomes stiff or locks
the brakes become stiff or fail
and the engine shuts off.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power and stalling of the engine can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and can lead to a loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: The engine stalls or loses power
the vehicle hesitates or struggles to accelerate
the check engine warning light illuminates
and the vehicle may experience a sudden loss of power steering and brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine damage, premature wear, and potentially cause the engine to seize, resulting in costly repairs.
symptoms: The vehicle consumes excessive amounts of oil between oil changes
with no visible signs of leaks or smoking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cooling system leaks can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage, premature wear, and potentially cause the engine to seize, resulting in costly repairs.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences a sudden loss of coolant
with no visible signs of leaks
and the temperature gauge may suddenly rise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Serpentine belt failure can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, and potentially cause accidents.
symptoms: The serpentine belt fails
causing the engine to stall or lose power
and the vehicle may experience a sudden loss of power steering and brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Air conditioning system failure can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioning system fails to operate
causing the vehicle to become hot and uncomfortable.
